Megan asked me to RP Iron Raptor for her untill she can post tomorrow.

::Prowl/IR::

Iron Raptor's back leg muscles tensed and then released, sending her 
sailing through the air at Menasor. She was trying to tackle him to 
the ground. Behind her, Prowl also jumps into the air, also heading 
for Menasor.





--- In nbwrpg@y..., Yanshosh@a... wrote:
> ::Prowl::
> 
> Prowl trots behind Iron Raptor, hearing her thoughts but making 
> little sense of them. All he knew was that there was prey to kill, 
> and as soon as IR pounced, so would he.
